    <h2>About Tiximo</h2>
    <p>Tiximo is an event discovery and recommendation service accessible via Telegram, WhatsApp, and Discord. It helps you find events near you and links you to third-party ticketing platforms to complete purchases.</p>
    <p>By using Tiximo you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the service.</p>
