  <section>
    <h2>What Tiximo is (and isn't)</h2>
    <p>Tiximo is a discovery layer — not a ticketing platform. We do not sell tickets, process payments, or control event listings. All ticket purchases are made directly on the relevant provider's platform (Ticketmaster, Eventbrite, DICE, etc.) under their terms and conditions.</p>
    <p>We are not affiliated with, endorsed by, or partnered with any ticketing platform or event organiser. See our <a href="/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a> for full details.</p>
