    <p>Event data is sourced from third-party APIs and may not always be accurate, complete, or up to date. Always verify event details — including date, time, venue, and ticket availability — directly with the event organiser or ticketing platform before making any purchase.</p>
    <p>Tiximo accepts no liability for inaccurate event data, cancelled events, or changes made by organisers or ticketing platforms.</p>
